Lets Be Friends are a young act from London who have set the EDM world alight in just six short months.

Supporters include; Steve Angello, Steve Aoki, Fedde Le Grand, Krewella, Bl3nd, SKisM and more. 

Their first ever remix (for Felix Da Housecat) became a number one on the biggest EDM download stores. 

This success, and buzz surrounding their debut live show demo on Soundcloud has brought many global booking offers so expect to see Lets Be Friends headlining a large event near you soon!
